{"tid":456133,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(求助)蜜月遊，打算瑞士加奧捷","createTime":"2017-11-02T16:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T02:49:16.000Z","uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c62e42d1aaed9157a5cd2faed425785db74f408","tid":456133,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:49:10.000Z","msg":"幫朋友查詢，求各位大大指點。<br />\n因為佢地29/11 就去渡蜜月，<br />\n但太忙無時間細plan.<br />\n上網見好少冬天時間去瑞士post<br />\n唔敢肯定去到有無野睇。<br />\n<br />\n行程如下<br />\n<br />\n(1) 瑞士<br />\n29/11 中午到Zurich  <br />\n1-4/12 Interlaken + Grindelwald + Bern<br />\n- 主要少女峰朝聖, 但怕天氣差<br />\n- 有時間遊下Thunersee湖<br />\n- 其實住係 Grindelwald 係咪正啲？<br />\n4/12 去Luzern <br />\n-  唔知上唔上到 Rigi / Pilatus / Titlis<br />\n6/12 返去zurich 坐Rj 去奧地利<br />\n*應該買8日pass（超貴，由Zurich去Bern先買，得唔得？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(2) 奧地利<br />\n6/12 預計都要中午先到 Salzburg <br />\n7/12 去國王湖即日來回<br />\n8/12 早上去Hallstatt<br />\n9/12 ice cave + five fingers<br />\n10/12 坐ck shuttle 去Cesky Krumlov <br />\n<br />\n(3) 捷克<br />\n1012 中午到ck 小鎮<br />\n11/12 中午去布拉格<br />\n12-13/12 行下城堡，買下野<br />\n14/12 坐飛機返香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求巴絲打指點<br />\n冬天果邊有咩值得去<br />\n或者可能太凍無野睇<br />\n費事去到先柒<br />\n<br />\n利申：10月頭去完奧捷，<br />\n預計唔到12月咁寒又落雪既天氣<br />\n會有幾影響啲景點"},{"pid":"20e293c8305b032b0ed3edb1936c80bebfe466f6","tid":456133,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"點解凍就冇嘢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話大雪冇嘢睇就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蜜月都忙到冇時間睇不如去夏威夷布吉扑嘢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4fed21e5dd327a4bfb0902b7793d6772a777a55","tid":456133,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"住grindelwald係正好多<br />\n上唔上到山係無人知，出發前應該check清楚d野冬天開唔開<br />\n<br />\n另外冬天國王湖係去唔到上湖，只係去到洋蔥教堂"},{"pid":"ef16f072ff28e11af53a70fed5b15823b0a9e637","tid":456133,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"另外你只係去呢堆地方，瑞士應該買half price card而唔係swiss pass<br />\n<br />\n計下條數應該係會抵d"},{"pid":"5fe104cbc5fbbb76c87593c4ee22b365970a0d4f","tid":456133,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:19:49.000Z","msg":"瑞士你依家睇下有冇啲早鳥飛賣，連半價卡會好平<br />\n<br />\n住grindewald 可以上埋first<br />\n果度有條橋伸出去，都幾正架"},{"pid":"a691c5ffb6165fbb7e19da474444ee15592c58f1","tid":456133,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解凍就冇嘢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話大雪冇嘢睇就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蜜月都忙到冇時間睇不如去夏威夷布吉扑嘢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSor 語癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係想講大雪<br />\n佢想睇雪嘛未睇過<br />\n慘呀兩公婆份工都係忙<br />\n幫到就幫下咁"},{"pid":"d6e2566458c444e86fdfb5badfca3118bfaf8667","tid":456133,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:23:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住grindelwald係正好多<br />\n上唔上到山係無人知，出發前應該check清楚d野冬天開唔開<br />\n<br />\n另外冬天國王湖係去唔到上湖，只係去到洋蔥教堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我要睇睇完，都唔知上邊座好。<br />\n少女峰就睇運氣啦<br />\n國王湖我知呀，不過去到st.xxx 都夠靚<br />\n個湖咪結冰就得"},{"pid":"3456ae736309383e284835f6f237e41408f66d23","tid":456133,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T17:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瑞士你依家睇下有冇啲早鳥飛賣，連半價卡會好平<br />\n<br />\n住grindewald 可以上埋first<br />\n果度有條橋伸出去，都幾正架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早鳥飛係指邊一樣野？ <br />\nGrindelwald 啲住宿 係though <a href=\"http://hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotel.com&d=NcqQRCZ2A5PjWhcJ3PxkfgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=47f6698d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hotel.com</a>果類都得呀嗎？？<br />\n<br />\n感謝"},{"pid":"a36d83bb471a2e1bba806d1c1336f67c7467c4ac","tid":456133,"uid":44377